title: Deposit Interest Rate in New Zealand
description: Deposit Interest Rate in New Zealand was at 3.35 percent on Thursday November 10. Deposit Interest Rate in New Zealand averaged 4.24 percent from 1981 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 16.32 percent in December of 1986 and a record low of -0.13 percent in December of 2020. The Deposit Interest Rate is the average rate paid by commercial banks to individuals or corporations on deposits. This page includes a chart with historical data for Deposit Interest Rate in New Zealand.
author: Reserve Bank of New Zealand
